{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"44bba8c094","title":"对宋××关于苏联专家问题报告的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a332fe808","index":0,"year":1958,"month":5,"day":16,"articleId":"44bba8c094","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958-1960卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui4a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fc648b5301","type":"title","text":"对宋××关于苏联专家问题报告的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"44bba8c094","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f5e2c8f27","type":"paragraph","text":"这是一个好文件，值得一读，请××××立即印发大会同志们，凡有苏联专家的地方，均应照此办理，不许有任何例外。苏联专家都是好同志，有理总是讲得通的，不讲理，或者讲的不高明，因而双方隔离不通，责任在我们方面。就共产主义队伍来说，四海之内皆兄弟，一定把苏联同志看作自己人，大会之后，根据总路线同他们多谈，政治挂帅，尊重苏联专家同志，刻苦虚心学习。但一定要破除迷信，打倒贾桂！贾桂（即奴才）是谁也看不起的。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"44bba8c094","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d56ee1e5fc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"44bba8c094","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"17bc665b25","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五八年五月十六日启","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui4","articleId":"44bba8c094","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":140,"end":140}}}},"__N_SSG":true}